Constant Force at 0.5 force units.(34.7385 pN)

data <- read_csv("~/Research/data/apr04/force0.5.csv", col_types = "idcc")

First I want to see two basic graph.

Distance vs Steps.

data %>% 
  filter(name == "wt") %>% 
  ggplot() +
  aes(Steps, Distance, color = run) +
  geom_line()

Histogram of Distance.

Then let’s see a206g.

Distance vs Steps.

Histogram of Distance for a206g.

data %>% filter(name == "wt") %>%  group_by(run) %>% count()
